name: MotivateMe
0:
”Alexa, open Motivate Me.”
”Alexa, ask Motivate Me for a quote.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: motivate me
des: Motivational quotes, facts, and stories from all walks of life; from celebrities and anonymous persons alike. Just shout, "Motivate Me", and you'll be given an inspirational quote by one of the world's many great minds.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
